OL,3,CFears that a church will have to close
OL,4,Cdue to pothole-filled access road
OL,6,FThe condition of the road to St
OL,7,FPeter's makes car travel difficult.
OL,9,FThe vicar of a rural west Cumbrian
OL,10,Fchurch says he fears it may soon have
OL,11,Fto close its doors to worshippers
OL,12,Fbecause of the state of the road
OL,13,Fleading to it.
OL,15,FSt Peter's Church in Camerton, near
OL,16,FWorkington, sits on the banks of the
OL,17,FRiver Derwent, and is surrounded by
OL,18,Fthe river on three sides.
