OL,3,CFears that a church will have to close
OL,4,Cdue to pothole-filled access road
OL,6,FThe only access to the site, which has
OL,7,Fbeen a place of worship since the 11th
OL,8,Fcentury, is a single track road.
OL,10,FReverend Ian Grainger is the parish
OL,11,Fpriest, and he says the state of the
OL,12,Faccess road has interfered with church
OL,13,Fservices and parishioners' worship.
OL,15,FRev Grainger told ITV Border: "We've
OL,16,Fhad hearses damaged, we've had the
OL,17,Fgeneral public's cars damaged... we
OL,18,Fhad a point where we had to say to
OL,19,Fpeople 'please do not bring your cars
OL,20,Fdown, it's just not safe'."
