OL,3,CFears that a church will have to close
OL,4,Cdue to pothole-filled access road
OL,6,FThe access problems are such that the
OL,7,Fcurate fears the potholed road could
OL,8,Fendanger the future of worship at the
OL,9,Fsite.
OL,11,FRev Grainger said: "If we don't have a
OL,12,Fdecent access, then there's a real
OL,13,Frisk to the future of the church,
OL,14,Fbecause people can't get there for
OL,15,Fregular acts of worship."
OL,17,FRob Steele, a former church warden,
OL,18,Fsays he has never before seen the road
OL,19,Fin such poor condition.
