OL,3,CFears that a church will have to close
OL,4,Cdue to pothole-filled access road
OL,6,FHe told ITV Border: "It hasn't been
OL,7,Fmaintained for as long as I can
OL,8,Fremember, and I can go back 40 or 50
OL,9,Fyears. This is the worst I've ever
OL,10,Fseen (the road)."
OL,12,FFellow parishioner Jim Mavir lost his
OL,13,Fwife 18 years ago, and tries to
OL,14,Fregularly visit her grave at St
OL,15,FPeter's.
OL,17,FHe said: "I need to get down here
OL,18,Fevery 7-10 days with fresh flowers,
OL,19,Fand something to cut the grass with,
OL,20,Fwhich in itself is quite a sad and
OL,21,Fsombre experience.
