OL,3,CFears that a church will have to close
OL,4,Cdue to pothole-filled access road
OL,6,F"When you have access problems, that
OL,7,Fintensifies the stress of the whole
OL,8,Fexperience."
OL,10,FParishioners have asked Cumberland
OL,11,FCouncil to repair the road, and while
OL,12,Ftheir pleas have resulted in temporary
OL,13,Frepairs from volunteers, they say the
OL,14,Fcouncil seems unwilling to take over
OL,15,Froad maintenance.
OL,17,FMr Steele said: "It has been taken
OL,18,Fover by the council as a byway open to
OL,19,Fall traffic. Now the council say that
OL,20,Fthey will only maintain it for horses,
OL,21,Fhorse-drawn vehicles, and pedestrians."
