OL,3,CFears that a church will have to close
OL,4,Cdue to pothole-filled access road
OL,6,FResponding to the concerns, Cumberland
OL,7,FCouncil said: "Due to persistent rain,
OL,8,Fthe Council has taken the decision to
OL,9,Fclose the public right of way to St
OL,10,FPeter's Church.
OL,12,F"It has come to light that works
OL,13,Finstructed and carried out by a third
OL,14,Fparty have been washed away leaving
OL,15,Fthe route impassible on foot.
OL,17,F"We have a number of properties that
OL,18,Fhave either flooded already or are in
OL,19,Fdanger of flooding and this has to be
OL,20,Four top priority.
